@startuml
title Ingest 共享状态机（L2 权威图）

' Scope:
' - 唯一状态与合法迁移定义
' Not in scope:
' - 不展开 API 细节与时序实现
' See also:
' - ../execution/ingest-execution-delete-sequence.puml
' - ../execution/ingest-execution-reprocess-sequence.puml
' - ../acceptance/ingest-acceptance-status-sequence.puml

left to right direction
hide empty description
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ArrowColor #2F3B4A
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
  BorderColor #4B5563
  FontColor #111827
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDEA
  BorderColor #A3A3A3
  FontColor #222222
}

state UPLOADED
state INGESTING
state INDEXED
state FAILED
state DELETING
state DELETED

[*] --> UPLOADED : 上传受理落库

' 布局锚点（不表达语义）
UPLOADED -[hidden]up-> INGESTING
INGESTING -[hidden]right-> INDEXED
UPLOADED -[hidden]down-> FAILED
UPLOADED -[hidden]right-> DELETING
INDEXED -[hidden]down-> DELETING
DELETING -[hidden]right-> DELETED

UPLOADED --> INGESTING : Worker 抢占（CAS）
INGESTING --> INDEXED : 处理成功
INGESTING --> FAILED : 处理失败

FAILED --> UPLOADED : Reprocess 成功
INDEXED --> UPLOADED

UPLOADED --> DELETING : Delete + CAS
FAILED --> DELETING
INDEXED --> DELETING
DELETING --> DELETED : 源文件与向量清理成功

DELETING --> UPLOADED : 删除失败回滚
DELETING --> FAILED
DELETING --> INDEXED

note top of INGESTING
Delete/Reprocess 在 INGESTING 阶段返回 409
end note

note right of DELETED
软删除终态（status 可观测）
重复删除幂等返回 204
end note

@enduml
